@startuml
title 微型智能产线核心类图

skinparam defaultFontName Noto Sans CJK SC
skinparam shadowing false

class WorkstationDevice {
  +deviceId: String
  +deviceType: String
  +status: String
  +faultCode: String
  +lastHeartbeat: DateTime
  +register()
  +heartbeat()
  +executeCommand(cmd)
}

class ProductionResource {
  +resourceId: String
  +name: String
  +type: String
  +value: String
  +updatedAt: DateTime
  +refresh(value)
}

class GatewayNode {
  +forwardMessage(topic, payload)
  +cacheMessage(msg)
  +filterAbnormalMessage(msg)
}

class PlatformNode {
  +registerDevice(device)
  +updateResource(resource)
  +judgeAlarm(device)
  +sendCommand(deviceId, cmd)
}

class EventRecord {
  +eventId: String
  +level: String
  +content: String
  +createdAt: DateTime
}

class DashboardView {
  +showOverview()
  +showTrend()
  +showEventList()
}

WorkstationDevice "1" o-- "0..*" ProductionResource : 拥有
PlatformNode ..> WorkstationDevice : 管理
PlatformNode ..> ProductionResource : 管理
PlatformNode ..> EventRecord : 生成
GatewayNode ..> WorkstationDevice : 接入/转发
DashboardView ..> PlatformNode : 读取展示数据

@enduml